{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-compound-finals/task-4","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Slušao/la sam zvukove i vežbovao/la sam izgovaranje spojenih završetaka i slogova.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-compound-finals","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">ei</span> je kraj druge kombinacije. Da bi se proizveo zvuk, počnite sa ustima koje su u zvučnoj poziciji <span class=\"highlighted-text\">e</span>, zatim polako pomerite jezik i usne ka poziciji <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span>.</p>\n<p>Odgovor bi trebalo da bude glatok, bez prekida između ova dva zvuka. <span class=\"highlighted-text\">e</span> se izgovara nešto duže, dok je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span> kratak i lagan, što uzrokuje prirodno spajanje umesto dve odvojene samoglasnike.</p>\n<p>Kada <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ei</span> je praćen početnim konsonantima, dobija slogove kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">bei</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">lei</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">fei</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">pei</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zei</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">shei</span>.</p>\n<p>Pokušajte da izgovorite ove slogove, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">fei</span> u različitim tonomima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Herufi</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">fēi</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">飞</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">féi</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">肥</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">fěi</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">匪</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">fèi</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">费</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-compound-finals/task-4"},"questions":[],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-center.png","characters":[{"character":"Lin Yating","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_pinyin_compound_finals.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":69.67,"finishTimestamp":96.2},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":1.73,"dialogue":{"text":"ei","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":3.19,"finishTime":4.05,"dialogue":{"text":"bei","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":5.49,"finishTime":6.36,"dialogue":{"text":"lei","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":7.84,"finishTime":8.88,"dialogue":{"text":"fei","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":10.53,"finishTime":11.48,"dialogue":{"text":"pei","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":13.53,"finishTime":14.34,"dialogue":{"text":"zei","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":16.36,"finishTime":17.38,"dialogue":{"text":"shei","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":19.12,"finishTime":20.02,"dialogue":{"text":"fēi","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null